4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT PROVIDING AN INCOME TAX BENEFIT FOR VOLUNTEER
5 FIREFIGHTERS AND VOLUNTEER EMERGENCY CARE PROVIDERS; PROVIDING A DEDUCTION FROM
6 TAXABLE INCOME; LIMITING THE DEDUCTION TO FULL-SERVICE VOLUNTEERS; PROVIDING FOR AN
7 ANNUAL INCREASE IN THE DEDUCTION BY AN INFLATION FACTOR; AMENDING SECTION 15-30-2120,
8 MCA; AND PROVIDING A DELAYED EFFECTIVE DATE AND AN APPLICABILITY DATE.”
